<a href="https://www.politico.com/story/2019/03/19/trump-democrat-oversight-investigation-congress-1225761" target="_top" class="js-tealium-tracking" data-tracking="mpos=inside body&amp;mid=ParentheticalModule&amp;lindex=Unknown&amp;lcol=Unknown">Trump officials prepared to stonewall Democratic oversight demands</a></h3>
</header>
